        "## Predicting AQI for New Cities\n",
        "\n",
        "Now, let's use our trained machine learning model to predict the AQI for several hypothetical cities with varying environmental conditions and geographical locations. This demonstrates the model's capability to generalize to unseen data."
      ]
    },
